### Scenario: Create a company organizational hierarchy with employees
### This demonstrates creating a hierarchical management structure:
### CEO -> VP of Engineering -> Team Managers -> Engineers

### Step 1: Create CEO
POST http://localhost:8080/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Alice",
  "lastName": "Johnson",
  "email": "alice.johnson@acme.com",
  "position": "CEO"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("ceoId", response.body.id);
%}

### Step 2: Create VP of Engineering
POST http://localhost:8080/employees
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bob",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "email": "bob.smith@acme.com",
  "position": "VP of Engineering",
  "managerId": {{ceoId}}
}

> {%
    client.global.set("vpEngId", response.body.id);
%}

