### Step 11: Get Platform Manager's direct reports
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/{{platformManagerId}}/subordinates

### Step 12: Get Frontend Manager's direct reports
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/{{frontendManagerId}}/subordinates

### Step 13: Get CEO's homepage (shows organizational context)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/{{ceoId}}/homepage

### Step 14: Get a mid-level employee's homepage (Platform Engineer)
GET http://localhost:8080/employees/{{platformEng1Id}}/homepage
